description.plain:
“Sick” is an unfinished song, which might be released soon. Puth performed it on Instagram Live on April 21, 2020 and told;

This is a song that I’m working on…. It’s not done yet, but I’m just working on it and am gonna play it early for you guys… Yea, it’s not done yet, it’s not out. I think I’m gonna put it out though

Charlie uploaded the video to YouTube where he wrote;

This is something I wrote to try and help the world heal a little. It’s called “Sick”…

https://youtu.be/xkr5X9Jpe_k

